## ğŸ§  **Why This Approach is Best for You (Beginner Perspective):**  
âœ… **Simple logic:** Just remember â€“ use a stack to find smaller elements efficiently.  
âœ… **Time Efficient:** O(n) â†’ Each element is pushed and popped at most once.  
âœ… **Space Efficient:** Uses extra space for the stack, but optimal for this problem.  
âœ… **Beginner-Friendly Comments:** You can easily revise this later and understand it.  

